		<div class='content'><div class="content" style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 22.7969px 57px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Georgia, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, KaiTi, 楷体, STKaiti, 华文楷体, serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><h2 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin: 0px; font-size: 30px;"><font face="impact" size="4" style="box-sizing: border-box;">很多学生分不清other，another，others，the other的区别</font></h2><h3 style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: inherit; margin: 0px; font-size: 24px;"><font size="4" face="times new roman" style="box-sizing: border-box;">我来告诉你，1分钟就够了！！！</font></h3><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><ol style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 44px;"><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">other单独只能作形容词，意思是另外的，修饰可数名词的复数</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">或不可数名词;</span></div></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">another 既可以作形容词又</span><font face="comic sans ms" style="box-sizing: border-box;">可以作代词。another表示很多</font><font face="comic sans ms" style="box-sizing: border-box;">中的另一个，也就是多选</font><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">1，</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">1/多</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">；</span></div></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Times;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">others只能作名词，others表示</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">很多中的另一些，属于多选多的类</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">型，即n/N（n&lt;N,n&gt;1)；</span></div></li><li style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><div style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Times;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;comic sans ms&quot;;">the other既可作形容词又可以作名词 指两个中的另一个，属于2选1，1/2</span></div></li></ol><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font face="comic sans ms" style="box-sizing: border-box;">我们会尽快添加评论区，🈶️疑问的可以24小时随时问! 我们有问必答！</font></div></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font face="comic sans ms" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></font></div><div style="box-sizing: border-box;"><font face="comic sans ms" style="box-sizing: border-box;">Feel Free to contact me at 13974936884</font></div><div id="2"><font face="comic sans ms" style="box-sizing: border-box;"><br></font></div></div>	  </div>
